Adrian R'Mante ( born February 3 , 1978 ) is an actor best known for his role as Esteban Ram√≠rez on the Disney Channel show The Suite Life of Zack and Cody . R'Mante also occasionally works as a substitute teacher . R'Mante is a native of Florida , born in Tampa . He currently lives in greater Los Angeles metropolitan area . He graduated from the University of Central Florida with a bachelor 's degree in Theatre Performance . He got his first break as the host for the game show Game Lab in Orlando , Florida . He has also hosted other shows on Nickelodeon and the Discovery Channel . He is also well known for being a minor character on the once - popular ( now cancelled ) show , Summerland . He is currently playing Esteban on The Suite Life of Zack and Cody with Cole and Dylan Sprouse . He was also a guest star in the second episode of season six of 24 ( TV Series ) . This biographical article related to television in the United States is a stub . 